# SuperAI Minecraft Bot - Project Structure

## Project Overview
This is a Minecraft Forge mod that provides a gRPC API for AI agents to interact with Minecraft. The main entry point is [SuperAIMod.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/SuperAIMod.java).

## Package Structure

The project follows a modular architecture:

- **`com.supermc.ai`** - Root package
  - **`common/`** - Shared utilities, constants ([SuperAIConstants.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/common/SuperAIConstants.java)), and exceptions ([SuperAIException.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/common/SuperAIException.java))
  - **`config/`** - Configuration management ([SuperAIConfig.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/config/SuperAIConfig.java))
  - **`grpc/`** - gRPC service implementations
    - `service/` - Core gRPC services (EnvironmentService, PlayerControlService, InventoryService, AIAgentService)
    - `proto/` - Generated protobuf classes
    - `interceptor/` - gRPC interceptors
  - **`environment/`** - Environment perception system
    - `scanner/` - World scanning logic
    - `analyzer/` - Environment analysis
    - `cache/` - Environment data caching
  - **`player/`** - Player control system
    - `controller/` - Player action control
    - `state/` - Player state management
    - `inventory/` - Inventory management

## Key Files

- **Main Mod Class**: [SuperAIMod.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/SuperAIMod.java) - Entry point, initializes all systems
- **Configuration**: [SuperAIConfig.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/config/SuperAIConfig.java) - Forge config spec with all settings
- **Constants**: [SuperAIConstants.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/common/SuperAIConstants.java) - All constant values
- **Proto Definition**: [superai.proto](mdc:src/main/proto/superai.proto) - gRPC API contract
- **Build Config**: [build.gradle](mdc:build.gradle) - Gradle build configuration with protobuf plugin

