## Configuration

Configuration is managed through Forge's config system. All config values are defined in [SuperAIConfig.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/supermc/ai/config/SuperAIConfig.java) and can be modified in `config/superai.toml` at runtime.

## gRPC Services

The mod exposes four main gRPC services defined in [superai.proto](mdc:src/main/proto/superai.proto):
1. **EnvironmentService** - World scanning and perception
2. **PlayerControlService** - Player action execution
3. **InventoryService** - Inventory management
4. **AIAgentService** - Agent registration and management
